{"tid":399655,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點算好，啊媽話想買樓","createTime":"2017-09-14T06:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T21:20:21.000Z","uid":145617,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58e89958b6dedc9d9af7d7e065e3dfb24bc3484d","tid":399655,"uid":145617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"今日啊媽打比我<br />\n忽然話想買樓，但係要用我個名，叫我去簽名<br />\n<br />\n首期成60萬<br />\n層樓好似400幾萬<br />\n但得300幾呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己屋企又唔係有錢<br />\n比得起首期都供得好食力<br />\n我覺得根本供唔起<br />\n細佬重讀緊中學，都要留翻啲錢比佢讀大學<br />\n<br />\n佢忽然話想買真係嚇親，佢又無同我同啊爸商量<br />\n唔知佢係唔係比人呃，<br />\n好似撞邪咁<br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢癡左線，竟然想用400萬買300呎<br />\n同點解要用我個名買？<br />\n咁係唔係要用我名同銀行借錢？<br />\n我重讀緊大學，就算想供都供唔起<br />\n就算我唔肯去簽名，佢應該都會一意孤行去買<br />\n<br />\n加上香港現時樓價買樓真係好癡線<br />\n我唔識買樓嘅嘢<br />\n如果跌係唔係就變負資產？<br />\n好驚佢真係買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點樣可以令佢放棄呢個念頭？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7182402499fedb9ed9fd2dcf7e382316a06c1644","tid":399655,"uid":66496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"即刻同你老豆傾下啦"},{"pid":"edaafa838079e6db94efa17166f34534b5fa59e2","tid":399655,"uid":45285,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:59:01.000Z","msg":"請開家庭會議，保證所有持份者得悉有關事宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84157b9b4670e129496b0d6be2f3be52be76f789","tid":399655,"uid":61832,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯標題跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51ac55540da3b7aff45d95996de3bbefab1df0d","tid":399655,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc